import React from 'react';
import PieChart from './PieChart';
import SchoolBarGraph from './bar';
import ReligionPieChart from './ReligionPieChart';
import CastePieChart from './CastePieChart';
import { Card, CardContent, Typography, Grid } from '@mui/material';

const ChartsCard = () => {
  return (
    <Card variant="outlined" style={{ margin: '16px' }}>
      <CardContent>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          Charts
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card variant="outlined">
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Dropout Pie Chart
                </Typography>
                <CastePieChart />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card variant="outlined">
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  School Bar Graph
                </Typography>
                <SchoolBarGraph />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card variant="outlined">
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Religion Pie Chart
                </Typography>
                <ReligionPieChart />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card variant="outlined">
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Caste Pie Chart
                </Typography>
                <CastePieChart />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}

export default ChartsCard;
